  <name>FreeOrion</name>
  <summary>Turn-based space empire and galactic conquest game</summary>
  <developer_name>FreeOrion Project</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>FreeOrion is a free, Open Source, turn-based space empire and galactic conquest computer game.</p>
    <p>FreeOrion is inspired by the tradition of the Master of Orion games, but does not try to be a clone or remake of that series or any other game. It builds on the classic 4X (eXplore, eXpand, eXploit and eXterminate) model.</p>
  </description>
